{"id":"125cae7c-f2c1-4b0a-90dc-4591a2728387","name":"Natsuki - Doki Doki Literature Club","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(222, 173, 237); color: inherit;\">THIS IS MY SECOND DDLC BOT</mark></u></strong></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>This time, it's the annoying one. Nah, I don't hate her. Even IF she is my least favorite character, I still find her INFINITELY more appealing than any other tsundere I've seen in media.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>NO ONE IS SELF-AWARE! THIS TAKES PLAC IN THE HIGH SCHOOL SETTING! I didn't like what I did with my last bot. I was just sick of writing characters in high school at the time. Also, the uniforms are programmed in this time. 👍</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/8alt2UjPRk2sZUi2embFc.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(222, 173, 237); color: inherit;\">INTROS!</mark></u></strong></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(222, 173, 237); color: inherit;\">1. Club Start!</mark></u></strong></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(222, 173, 237); color: inherit;\">2. Home Start!</mark></u></strong></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(222, 173, 237); color: inherit;\">3. Bedroom Start!</mark></u></strong></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(222, 173, 237); color: inherit;\">4. FINE! Do it yourself then you- you idiot! =)</mark></u></strong></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(222, 173, 237); color: inherit;\">CHARACTERS!</mark></u></strong></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(120, 224, 126); color: inherit;\">Monika</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(71, 49, 117); color: inherit;\">Yuri</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(35, 114, 168); color: inherit;\">Sayori</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(222, 173, 237); color: inherit;\">Natsuki (duh)</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u>YOU!</u></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>(MC DOESN'T EXIST)</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>WARNING! YAP AHEAD!</strong></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Hey everyone! Thank you all for visiting! As I said previously, I will be going through my backburner. And I wanted to tackle this one first. I plan on doing the other dokis in the future, but we will see.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>This is hopefully better than my last one. I'm not super happy with how my Monika bot turned out. But I think this one turned out much better.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Now then, please enjoy!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Credits:</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Thumbnail: soresaki</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Game: Doki Doki Literature Club</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Bot: TheDenimSquid</strong></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"FJzWdj18SUL2iWDDP3Yta.webp","creator":"TheDenimSquid","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":112,"messages":767,"created_at":"2026-02-1